Module org.monarchinitiative.phenol.analysis
Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.analysis

Class StudySet

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.analysis.StudySet
All Implemented Interfaces:
ItemSet<TermId>
public class StudySet extends Object implements ItemSet<TermId>
This class holds all gene names of a study and their associated (optional) descriptions. The names are extracted directly by the constructor given study file. The class takes a list of genes in the constructor; the list can be for the population set or the study set. It stores these genes as the keys of annotationMap, and creates a map for each Gene Ontology term used to directly or indirectly annotate the genes; each gene is thereby associated with a list of all of the genes that annotate the terms.
Author:
Peter Robinson, Sebastian Bauer
